msg: Make svn_client_patch() enforce that the target is an existing directory.
Before this change, svn patch would simply skip all targets if the target
was a file or a non-existent path.
(svn_client_patch): Say that local_abspath is expected to be a directory.
(svn_client_patch): Provide reasonable error messages when the target
does not exist or is not a directory.
